76561198071144948,Recommended,322500,35458330,Posted: 3 October,all,Raken,"Ever want to feel like some kind of sci fi/action hero who shoots, slices, and beats up baddies?Ever want to pull off long kill chains with different weapons, all while dodging bullets like a boss?Ever want to feel like the one?This is the game for you then.The main mechanic of this game is the ability to control time by the movement of your character. At a stand still everything is in slow motion, allowing you to plan out your approach. ""Time moves when you move"" That being said every movement and action causes time to run normally, which makes it important for you to think before going into action. While dodging pass zooming bullets you'll be given different tools to dispatch the foes that stand in your way. Some of those tools being: Fire-arms, melee weapons, and even the work-phone in your cubicle.The gameplay is great, but the game itself does not contain a lotYou're given a short, not so compelling story; with a few interesting twists. There are other side modes you can play, but sadly not enough content to keep you hooked.The gameplay is great, but with the small amount of content it contains it's not worth the high price the game is running onGet the game during a sale, where it's cheaper than it's current price."
