76561197966560234,Recommended,322500,31957600,Posted: 25 May,all,Korn Prime,"The game combines a pseudo-Matrix-ey story with action setpieces that are its main selling point. There is no overearching story, plot, or missions to be followed. You enter a setpiece, and the goal is to come out alive, using everything at your disposal.In SUPERHOT, time moves normally only when you do. When you stand still it moves ever so slowly, allowing you to plan your moves, dodge bullets, use the environment and sow mayhem in your wake, in an extremely minimal and utalitarian UI and visual style that acts as a nearly blank slate for your own interpretation. It sounds awesome, right?Well, it actually is. Sorry, no twist here."
